{"0":"All tasks completed successfully. Here's a summary of what was accomplished:\n\n---\n\n## ✅ 任务完成\n\n### 1. 重命名映射（Rename Mapping）\n- 从 65 篇 PDF 中提取了论文标题（使用 PyMuPDF 基于字体大小分析）\n- 处理了多种特殊格式：arXiv 预印本、ICLR 小型大写字母、期刊头部信息等\n- 将所有文件复制到 `/tmp_workspace/results/papers/`（扁平结构）\n- 空格和斜杠均替换为 `_`\n\n### 2. 分类（Classification）\n65 篇论文分入 6 个类别：\n- **Multimodal / Vision-Language Models**：14 篇\n- **Medical Image Analysis**：9 篇  \n- **Image / Video Generation & Editing**：12 篇\n- **Autonomous Driving / Robotics / Embodied AI**：3 篇\n- **3D Vision / Reconstruction / Gaussian Splatting**：8 篇\n- **Others**：19 篇\n\n### 3. Caption 相关论文与表格提取\n找到 **2 篇** caption 相关论文：\n\n1. **Asymmetric Idiosyncrasies in Multimodal Models** — 研究 caption 模型的风格特征及其对文生图系统的影响。Table 2 列出了每个 captioning 模型（Claude、Gemini、GPT-4o、Qwen3-VL）的 Top-10 TF-IDF 特征短语。\n\n2. **CAPRL: STIMULATING DENSE IMAGE CAPTION CAPABILITIES VIA REINFORCEMENT LEARNING** — 通过强化学习提升 LVLM 的密集图像描述能力。Table 2 展示了不同预训练数据集（ShareGPT4V-1M、DenseFusion-1M 及其 CapRL 标注版本）在 12 个基准测试上的消融实验结果。","_meta":{"runtime":"node","runtimeVersion":"22.22.1","hostname":"89dbf4884b39","name":"openclaw","date":"2026-06-27T15:22:36.643Z","logLevelId":3,"logLevelName":"INFO","path":{"fullFilePath":"file:///usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975:46","fileName":"subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js","fileNameWithLine":"subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975","fileColumn":"46","fileLine":"975","filePath":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js","filePathWithLine":"/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DVwhOlEq.js:975","method":"console.log"}},"time":"2026-06-27T15:22:36.643+00:00"}
